  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Physician Pursuit:</strong> 6th and 11th level</em></p>\n<p>Whenever you expend superiority dice to restore hit points or grant temporary hit points to a creature, you can roll an additional die [[/r d6]] and add it to the roll. This die increases to [[/r d8]] at 9th level, [[/r d10]] at 13th level, and [[/r d12]] at 17th level.</p>\n<p>Additionally, whenever you expend superiority dice to restore hit points or grant temporary hit points to a creature, if the creature is the target of your Critical Analysis, you can instead choose the maximum on both dice. Once you've used this feature, you must finish a short or long rest before you can use it again. Starting at 11th level, you can use it twice before a rest, but only once on the same turn.</p>",
